{"tid":2196511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：警方半年發3,500限聚令告票僅撤回3宗 有差不多2千人已交罰款","createTime":"2020-09-10T03:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-10T10:39:10.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"904efb2bda9f2aa5aba90d4f24684a1d6be6460e","tid":2196511,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-10T03:31:01.000Z","msg":"限聚令實施後的半年內，警方透過限聚令截查及票控巿民的做法備受質疑，而在警方發出近3,500宗罰款告票中，至今只撤回3宗。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》向警方查詢，逾半年間共撤銷多少限聚令檢控，警方發言人今天回覆指，經警方中央交通違例檢控組處理的定額罰款通知書共3,498張，已繳交罰款的共1,948張，而經警方審視後，共撤回3張定額罰款通知書，相信是太古城獲撤控的一家三口。<br />\n警方並指，其餘的定額罰款通知書，如於限期前仍未繳交罰款，中央交通違例檢控組會作出跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200910/PBVG7W4WWVFGNHI2TLSVFWH3IQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0Fpw8YYlWJoKSm1mjlA23C4_klBVQkc44ke4Xdx8ceUtD5EiTtwGST9wM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200910%2FPBVG7W4WWVFGNHI2TLSVFWH3IQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0Fpw8YYlWJoKSm1mjlA23C4_klBVQkc44ke4Xdx8ceUtD5EiTtwGST9wM&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE6ooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=6aed4c05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200910%2FPBVG7W4WWVFGNHI2TLSVFWH3IQ%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0Fpw8YYlWJoKSm1mjlA23C4_klBVQkc44ke4Xdx8ceUtD5EiTtwGST9wM&h=9de4e8f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200910/PBVG7W4WWVFGNHI2TLSVFWH3IQ/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0Fpw8YYlWJoKSm1mjlA23C4_klBVQkc44ke4Xdx8ceUtD5EiTtwGST9wM</a>"},{"pid":"20febad74a5bc669f81a9fefb9919e918b6751cd","tid":2196511,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0